{"id":83161,"title":"[Parodontocid efficiency in complex treatment and prevention of gingivitis].","abstract":"Antiplaque/antigingivitis effect of an alcohol-free mouthrinse Parodontocid were evaluated by randomized parallel group clinical trial. Sixty patients with gingivitis were clinically examined to determine PHP, RMNPI and PMA indexes. After professional dental prophylaxis, subjects were randomly assigned in two groups to 10 days oral hygiene program. Group 1 patients used only toothbrush and prophylactic toothpaste while in group 2 persons used Parodontocid in conjunction with normal brushing and flossing.Parodontocid significantly reduced plaque and gingivitis compared to negative control. ","date":"2014-01-16","categories":"Stomatognathic Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24429785","annotations":[{"name":"Oral hygiene","weight":0.877753,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oral_hygiene"},{"name":"Clinical trial","weight":0.792698,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clinical_trial"},{"name":"Hygiene","weight":0.786341,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hygiene"},{"name":"Dentistry","weight":0.711571,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dentistry"},{"name":"Gingivitis","weight":0.650072,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gingivitis"},{"name":"Randomized controlled trial","weight":0.633295,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Randomized_controlled_trial"},{"name":"Mouth","weight":0.524904,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mouth"},{"name":"Prophylaxis","weight":0.426019,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prophylaxis"},{"name":"Preventive medicine","weight":0.368093,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Preventive_medicine"},{"name":"Toothpaste","weight":0.316275,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Toothpaste"},{"name":"Scientific control","weight":0.273167,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wik